1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Siyali hands over Utkarsh's frog which he believes is his mother's reincarnation. Meanwhile, Parth gets suspended from the school for hitting two students. The mother superior insists Siyali attempt the scholarship test to try and get into Warrior High.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Parth is very upset after a big argument with Pankaj. His mother consoles him and tells him that his father wanted him to study at Warrior High. Meanwhile, Siyali tries to convince Neeti and Utkarsh to prepare for the admission tests to Warrior high.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Anvesha hires Veebha Anand, an ex-student of Warrior High as an assistant teacher. Elsewhere, Parth's mother takes him to the exam centre for the scholarship exam to get admission at Warrior High. Utkarsh is seen leaving the exam hall.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Neeti and Utkarsh get selected for Warrior High. Utkarsh gets angry with Siyali but she justifies her act by saying that she has secured their future. Parth's mother fights with Pankaj as he hides his scholarship letter.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: Siyali gives her lucky charm to Utkarsh after he gives her a gift. Parth's mother pours gasoline on Pankaj and blackmails him to return the letter. Vibha lies that she has a car but then has to think of a way to give her friend a lift.

6.title: Episode #1.6
6.plot: All the students assemble at the Delhi station to board their train to Dehradun. It is a very emotional atmosphere as Siyali comes to drop Neeti and Utkarsh. She dreams of being a part of Warrior High with her friends.

7.title: Episode #1.7
7.plot: Siyali and Siddharth miss the train to Warrior High. Siddharth gets in trouble with the hitchhiker who gives them a lift and begs Siyali for help. Later, Parth gets agitated when Dishank taunts him by mocking his father.

8.title: Episode #1.8
8.plot: With her schoolmates making fun of her looks, Neeti is quite upset and breaks down. Her teacher comforts her, saying that self-belief is all that counts.

9.title: Episode #1.9
9.plot: Siddharth and Siyali roam around near the campus at night. Meanwhile, students get checked for mobile phones and beauty products. Utkarsh tries to make new friends and finally fits in.

10.title: Episode #1.10
10.plot: Ayaz and his mates turn off the lights as a plan to rag their juniors. All the students get scared and run across the campus. Siddharth and Siyali run into the library to hide and Siddhant tries to get close to Siyali.

11.title: Episode #1.11
11.plot: Vibha Ma'am gives a clue about finding answers in the library. They find a CD in which the FAB5 give them the clue to fight back against Night Call. The students get motivated to fight back against the seniors.

12.title: Episode #1.12
12.plot: When Siddharth thought he was winning, Ayaz catches him and takes him to the vice-Principal Urmila. She praises the seniors on their victory at the Night Call. Finally, she asks to meet Siddharth in her office.

13.title: Episode #1.13
13.plot: The principal, Anvesha Rajput delivers an inspiring speech and reveals the name of the winner of Night Call. It turns out to be Neeti of the junior batch who had hid under the principal's desk during the competition.

14.title: Episode #1.14
14.plot: Anvesha announces Neeti as a legend of Warrior High. Meanwhile, the staff gather in Anvesha's room and decide the theme of the fresher's party. Later, Kamini warns Veebha about not trying to snatch her position.

15.title: Episode #1.15
15.plot: Sid and Parth have a fight and the rest of the students decide on a face off in a boxing bout. Meanwhile, Veebha's friends and alumni of the school are on their way to Warrior High to attend the Fresher's party. Later, Kamini threatens Veebha.

16.title: Episode #1.16
16.plot: Manik and friends get into a clash with Ayaz and group. Both the groups challenge each other for a running race. Manik is in for a surprise when he learns that Veebha is the new dance teacher.

17.title: Episode #1.17
17.plot: The episode starts with the Fab Five performing the opening act at the fresher's party, followed by the junior's dance competition. Meanwhile, jealous Kamini sets a trap for Veebha.

18.title: Episode #1.18
18.plot: Parth shows immense bravery as he puts off the fire from Veebha's dress using his bare hands . Parth, Utkarsh, Neeti and Siyali are among the shortlisted students for the Warrior High Mr and Miss Fresher competition. Parth is selected for his brave act.

19.title: Episode #1.19
19.plot: Veebha is shocked to hear Ayaz's lie. Meanwhile, Urmila shouts at Siddharth for not choosing the science stream. Later, Ayaz and his friends plans to play a trick on Veebha, but Utkarsh tries to spoil the plan.

20.title: Episode #1.20
20.plot: Everyone gathers in a classroom and Ayaz asks Siddharth and Parth to choose partners for the boxing match. Elsewhere, Anvesha asks Urmila to put less pressure on Siddharth. Later, Anvesha is shocked to see the bracelet in Utkarsh's hand.

21.title: Episode #1.21
21.plot: Kamini tries to insult Veebha in the staff room. Meanwhile, Rishabh doesn't allow Parth to talk to his mother which makes him angry, but later Kamini gives him permission. Elsewhere, Krissane calls Siddharth to a room to celebrate their first kiss.

22.title: Episode #1.22
22.plot: Parth and Utkarsh take up a challenge with Siddharth and Charlie. When Krisann is criticizing and blaming Anjala for flirting with her boyfriend, Niti steals Krisann's phone to help Parth.

23.title: Episode #1.23
23.plot: The principle tries to find out the background details of Utkarsh, Anjala and Nitin. Meanwhile, the boxing match is about to start, but Parth is missing and Utkarsh ends up having to fight on his behalf.

24.title: Episode #1.24
24.plot: Utkarsh is brutally beaten up by Siddharth but he doesn't gives up. Siyali and Nitin watch helplessly. Later, Urmila saves Utkarsh and gets emotional when she recalls how she had abandoned Utkarsh and Siyali a long time ago.

25.title: Episode #1.25
25.plot: Parth sits by himself and misses Utkarsh. He regrets the impulsive decisions he made. Veebha consoles him asking him to think more rationally as his temper has made everything worse.

26.title: Episode #1.26
26.plot: Neeti and Siyali are happy to see that Utkarsh is okay. Urmila is torn between her love for Siddharth and Utkarsh. Siddharth asks her why she slapped him in front of everyone to which she answers that he should be worthy of his name.

27.title: Episode #1.27
27.plot: Vibha is shocked when Utkarsh tells her he will leave after his performance. When VIbha asks about his performance, Utkarsh says it will be a surprise. Later, Siddharth shocks Rohit by announcing that he will be participating in the competition.

28.title: Episode #1.28
28.plot: Rohit asks Dishank to lock the green room to stop Siddharth from participating but Sayali gets locked up with Siddharth by mistake. Later, Parth hears Sayali calling for help and breaks the lock of the green room.

29.title: Episode #1.29
29.plot: Siddharth, Siyali, Utkarsh and Neeti perform during the Freshers Party. Later, principal Anvesha Rajput declares Utkarsh Rajput as Mr. Fresher and Neeti Awasti as Ms. Fresher 2015.

30.title: Episode #1.30
30.plot: Utkarsh tells Siyali that he is very eager to go to Mumbai. Meanwhile Parth's father lies to the vice-principal about Parth's rustication from his previous school.

31.title: Episode #1.31
31.plot: All the students of Warrior High condemn Utkarsh, Siyali and Niti calling them losers and orphans. Niti consoles them, giving no heed to their words. Urmila gets emotional when she learns that Utkarsh calls a frog his mother.

32.title: Episode #1.32
32.plot: Veebha and Rishab discuss Anvesha Ma'am's brave decision. Kamini interrupts and taunts them, but Risabh shuts her up. The students ignore Niti and Siyali during the sports class.

33.title: Episode #1.33
33.plot: Utkarsh and Parth lose their temper and get into a fight. Urmila visits Utkarsh in hospital and becomes emotional. Later, Parth emotionally connects with Siyali and Siddharth.

34.title: Episode #1.34
34.plot: Krissane and her gang conspire against Siyali and invite her to Simi's birthday party. Utkarsh and Siyali try to persuade Neeti to come for the party, but she refuses. Siddharth gets jealous when Urmila buys Utkarsh the same gift she bought him.

35.title: Episode #1.35
35.plot: Parth accidentally runs into Veebha in the library. Parth and Veebha sense their growing affection toward each other after they share some eye to eye contact. Krissane tries to insult Siyali by playing a game of Question and Answer.

36.title: Episode #1.36
36.plot: Siyali is humiliated by Krissane and her friends at Simi's birthday party, Siddharth consoles her. Later, Rohit harasses Simi but Siyali and Siddharth come to her rescue. Rohit questions Siddharth about his relationship with Siyali.

37.title: Episode #1.37
37.plot: Veebha approaches few students for violating the rules and Urmila rebukes Kamini for not sticking to her responsibility. Meanwhile, Siyali yells at Utkarsh for watching vulgar movies. Later, Kamini asks some students to report to Urmila's office.

38.title: Episode #1.38
38.plot: When Urmila asks Rohit why he out of his dorm at midnight, Siyali reveals that the boys were in the AV room watching adult movies. Urmila then punishes the students by ordering them to clean the corridors and the classrooms for two weeks.

39.title: Episode #1.39
39.plot: Kamini conspires against Veebha to get her out of the school. Meanwhile, Siyali defends Simi when Krissane blames her for the punishment. Later, Utkarsh's friends blame him for the punishment.

40.title: Episode #1.40
40.plot: Kamini gets Veebha locked inside the washroom to frame her. But then she realizes that Parth got locked in instead of Siddharth. Later, Neeti gets Siyali to meet Utkarsh to sort their problems, but fails.

41.title: Episode #1.41
41.plot: Veebha and Parth are locked inside a bathroom. As they try to get closer, Utkarsh comes inside and Veebha goes away. Siddharth is helpless and asks Siyali for help in a test.

42.title: Episode #1.42
42.plot: Shushant is pressurised by his parents to learn science. Meanwhile, Utkarsh dreams about an angel who motivates him to win the boxing match. Siddhanth finds something unique about Siyali and is smitten by her. Krissane becomes extremely jealous.

43.title: Episode #1.43
43.plot: Krissane gives Siddharth a jersey with his name on it. After many attempts to get Utkarsh and Siyali to talk, Neeti and Parth make them sort out their differences. Later, Shushant and a senior have a fight in the boys' hostel over a girl.

44.title: Episode #1.44
44.plot: Neeti asks Siyali not to worry about Krissane's taunts and appreciates her for saving Simi's life. Meanwhile, Siyali regrets breaking her promises and consoles Utkarsh with Neeti's help. Later, Siddharth realizes that he is in love with Siyali.

45.title: Episode #1.45
45.plot: An earthquake takes place during the night and the students begin to panic. Utkarsh and Neeti look for Siyali who had gone to the mess to fill her bottle, when they hear a scream.

46.title: Episode #1.46
46.plot: Siddharth starts fantasizing about Siyali and sees her everywhere. But he ends up making a fool of himself.

47.title: Episode #1.47
47.plot: Utkarsh slaps Ayaz when he touches him inappropriately. Parth defends him against Siddhanth and his roommates. Ayaz's friends tell Utkarsh to go in search of Ayaz and lock him in the library as a part of Ayaz's plan for revenge.

48.title: Episode #1.48
48.plot: Utkarsh falls into Ayaz's trap in the library where Utkarsh apologizes for slapping him but he gives no heed to it and molests Utkarsh. Parth comes to his rescue. Later, Krissane and Ayaz team up to teach Utkarsh and his friends a lesson.

49.title: Episode #1.49
49.plot: Parth and Siddharth have to come in the way after Utkarsh attacks Ayaz. Later, Urmila has a stern word with Utkarsh and Ayaz regarding the incident.

50.title: Episode #1.50
50.plot: Krissane and her friends make fun of Utkarsh. Urmila hugs him while he cries and buries his frog. Later, Urmila declares Utkarsh and Krissane as the head boy and girl.

51.title: Episode #1.51
51.plot: Siddharth starts fantasizing about Siyali and sees her everywhere. But he ends up making a fool of himself.

52.title: Episode #1.52
52.plot: Utkarsh slaps Ayaz when he touches him inappropriately. Parth defends him against Siddhanth and his roommates. Ayaz's friends tell Utkarsh to go in search of Ayaz and lock him in the library as a part of Ayaz's plan for revenge.

53.title: Episode #1.53
53.plot: Utkarsh falls into Ayaz's trap in the library where Utkarsh apologizes for slapping him but he gives no heed to it and molests Utkarsh. Parth comes to his rescue. Later, Krissane and Ayaz team up to teach Utkarsh and his friends a lesson.

54.title: Episode #1.54
54.plot: Parth and Siddharth have to come in the way after Utkarsh attacks Ayaz. Later, Urmila has a stern word with Utkarsh and Ayaz regarding the incident.

55.title: Episode #1.55
55.plot: Krissane and her friends make fun of Utkarsh. Urmila hugs him while he cries and buries his frog. Later, Urmila declares Utkarsh and Krissane as the head boy and girl.

56.title: Episode #1.56
56.plot: Urmila announces a competition and selects Utkarsh's name for the competition which shocks Siddharth. However, Siddharth gets angry at her for selecting Utkarsh instead of him and decides to get selected from the students' side.

57.title: Episode #1.57
57.plot: Election campaigns for Head Boy and Head Girl of the school have begun. Neeti works hard for Siyali's campaign and Krissane tries to threaten Neeti. Later, Siddharth and Siyali argue over the deserving candidate for Head Boy, as Siyali supports Utkarsh.

58.title: Episode #1.58
58.plot: Urmila addresses the students in the assembly and announces the names of the students who are elected to compete against Krissane and Utkarsh. Siyali and Siddharth are the ones to get nominated by the students.

59.title: Episode #1.59
59.plot: Veebha conducts an IQ test for the students. Later, Urmila gathers everyone and announces that Utkarsh and Siyali are the head boy and the head girl respectively.

60.title: Episode #1.60
60.plot: Krissane argues with Siyali over the new rules of the school. Kamini warns Veebha about her job and challenges her to finish the Hindi exam paper. Siddharth plans a surprise party in his dorm and Charlie invites Neeti and Utkarsh to the party.

61.title: Episode #1.61
61.plot: Utkarsh is positive even though he lost the post of Head Boy and continues to spread his joy everywhere. Later, Parth gets bored and goes to the library to meet Veebha ma'am and spends some time with her.

62.title: Episode #1.62
62.plot: The girls hide their party plans from Siyali. Later, when Siddharth comes to the party Neeti changes the music starting a dance off between Siddharth and Utkarsh. Finally, Siyali walks in and stops the music.

63.title: Episode #1.63
63.plot: Siyali yells at Siddharth, Utkarsh and others for organizing a party in the school premises. Siddharth apologizes to her and gets her to join the party. Veebha finds Parth and takes him inside the library where he flatters her in his drunk state.

64.title: Episode #1.64
64.plot: In the middle of the night, hearing some loud noise, Kamini walks up to the door. On noticing Kamini, the gate keeper informs the students who were partying in the hostel premises. Later, Kamini notices Siddharth missing.

65.title: Episode #1.65
65.plot: Kamini performs a surprise visit and checks the rooms of the students at night. Siddharth gets furious and shocked when Parth thrashes and blames him for mixing alcohol in his drink. Later, Parth bunks the English class due to his guilt.

66.title: Episode #1.66
66.plot: Neeti and Utkarsh try to console Parth as he is really upset that he had consumed alcohol. Later, Parth says he has broken the promise he made to his mother and wants to be forgiven. Meanwhile, Siyali gets angry at Siddharth for mixing alcohol in Parth's drink.

67.title: Episode #1.67
67.plot: When Siddharth and Parth get into a fight with each other, Siddharth's friends hit Parth brutally. Meanwhile, Utkarsh runs to look for help and finds Anvesha.

68.title: Episode #1.68
68.plot: A physical fight between Siddharth and Parth creates chaos at Warrior High. Therefore, Anvesha takes drastic measures to discipline the students and removes Siddharth from the Head Boy's position.

69.title: Episode #1.69
69.plot: Veebha recollects her moments with Parth. Meanwhile, Anvesha calls for Siddharth and his group in order to punish them. She orders them to clean all the toilets with toothbrushes for violating the rules.

70.title: Episode #1.70
70.plot: Anvesha punishes Siddharth and his friends for their misbehavior. Later, Urmila tries to console Siddharth while Parth goes to the staff room to meet Veebha. Elsewhere, Utkarsh looks for Neeti to deliver a letter from Charlie.

71.title: Episode #1.71
71.plot: Siyali learns about Neeti's love for Charlie and asks Neeti to stay away from Charlie, as he was one of Siddharth's friends. Meanwhile, Siddharth and his friends make fun of Neeti's feelings, when she confesses her love for Charlie in the classroom.

72.title: Episode #1.72
72.plot: Charlie hurts Neeti by playing with her feelings. Siddharth and his group of friends rag Neeti and insult Siyali as well. Angela, the new entrant in school saves Neeti and Siyali and becomes the envy of the school due to her smartness.

73.title: Episode #1.73
73.plot: Neeti cries over Charlie, she believed he'd truly adore her but he didn't. Anvesha informs the Tagore house about their performance and orders them to prepare for midterm exams, she also introduces Angela to them.

74.title: Episode #1.74
74.plot: Siyali and Neeti praise Utkarsh. Meanwhile, Veebha conducts a dance class for the girls and Utkarsh has an argument with Charlie. Elsewhere, Parth tries to share his feelings with Veebha.

75.title: Episode #1.75
75.plot: Kamini punishes the students and also announces about their Hindi weekly exam. Later, while supervising the examination room, Kamini finds a crushed paper ball near Siddharth's feet and stops him from attending the exam.

76.title: Episode #1.76
76.plot: Siddharth makes Charlie confront Neeti and confess his love for her. Meanwhile, Charlie reveals that his father was a patient of dwarfism. He also affirms that he is too scared to date Neeti for the same reason.

77.title: Episode #1.77
77.plot: Kamini denies Veebha her leave to go home on her birthday. Meanwhile, Parth convinces Siyali to let him go out of the school to buy Veebha a gift. Krissane tries to steal Angela's diary but Angels tells her that she will never find it.

78.title: Episode #1.78
78.plot: Siyali steals the main gate keys for Parth to sneak out of the schoolhouse. Later, Utkarsh involves Angela in the secret party plan and Angela blackmails Siyali to organize a private party in the school. Meanwhile, Krissane breaks up with Siddharth.

79.title: Episode #1.79
79.plot: Parth and the other students throw a surprise birthday party for Veebha and he invites Veebha's grandmother it. Krissane gets jealous with Angela spending time with Utkarsh. Meanwhile, Krissane reads Angela's diary and finds out her secret.

80.title: Episode #1.80
80.plot: Parth fights with the goons and saves Veebha, Later, he reveals his feelings for her. Meanwhile, Siddharth finds Siyali in the library and confesses his feelings to her and also tells her that he will stand by her in any state of affair.

81.title: Episode #1.81
81.plot: Angela faints and Krissane reveals to everyone that Angela has HIV. Angela's friends and the faculty members are upset. Dr. Mehra tells the students to be normal and not to believe in the myths about HIV.

82.title: Episode #1.82
82.plot: Utkarsh decides to support Angela and he tries to revive her spirits, he also encourages her and tries to eradicate her fear of AIDS. Meanwhile, Krissane and Siyali team up, and confront Siddharth.

83.title: Episode #1.83
83.plot: Krissane and Angela have a catfight over Utkarsh. Meanwhile, Parth confesses his love for Veebha in the library and she slaps him. Later, Neeti tricks Siddharth into wearing a classical dance costume and makes a fool out of himself to impress Siyali.

84.title: Episode #1.84
84.plot: Parth's mother is against Veebha and Parth's relationship and complains about her to Urmila. Parth defends Veebha and takes the blame on himself. Siddharth and Krissane confess their love to Siyali and Utkarsh.

85.title: Episode #1.85
85.plot: After seeing Siddharth with Siyali, Utkarsh fights with him. Later, Utkarsh sacrifices his love after he finds out that Siddharth is his brother. On the other hand, Veebha quits her job to stop Parth from getting suspended.

imdb.title: MTV Warrior High
plot: _MTV Warrior High_ (qv) is an Indian television show aimed at a young audience, which is broadcast on MTV India. The story revolves around a group of students at Warrior High, a boarding school in Dehradun, India.::Dibyayan_Chakravorty
